Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:30.25,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}看起來又有精氣神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:30.55,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}是呢
